CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 16, 1973, pg. 22 reads: "Harty Bible Graduates - After completing the prescribed four-year Bible Study Course at Harty Bible these graduates were formally presented in commencement exercises recently. Left to right, they are, Clifton B. Pope, Ms. Beatrice L. Shelton, Viola M. Vaughn, Rema L. Pooe, Miriam A. White and Floyd L. Palmer, class president. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Harty Bible graduates, from left: Clifton B. Pope, Beatrice L. Shelton, Viola M. Vaughn, Rema L. Pooe, Miriam A. White, and Floyd L. Palmer, standing before altar in Christian Tabernacle Church
